sur la conscience.

538
00:48:43,460 --> 00:48:46,420
- De simples ouvriers.
- On a pigé, Esme.

539
00:48:46,860 --> 00:48:48,180
Elle a raison.

540
00:48:48,980 --> 00:48:50,860
Comme Arthur,
tu porteras ce poids.

541
00:48:54,300 --> 00:48:56,620
En espérant que la maison
que tu t'offriras

542
00:48:57,060 --> 00:48:58,900
deviendra un lieu de

543
00:48:59,740 --> 00:49:00,780
méditation.

544
00:49:02,540 --> 00:49:04,180
De rédemption, même.

545
00:49:09,220 --> 00:49:10,260
Charlie,

546
00:49:10,340 --> 00:49:14,020
