et les sages paroles de Curly.

547
00:49:14,900 --> 00:49:18,020
Johnny, pour le vivre et le couvert.

548
00:49:19,900 --> 00:49:20,980
Lizzie.

549
00:49:27,380 --> 00:49:28,380
Michael.

550
00:49:29,580 --> 00:49:30,660
Pour les meurtres.

551
00:49:32,140 --> 00:49:33,340
